data.description: Amazingly well cared for home with loads of potential. Spacious home with above level daylight basement. Enter to large foyer and remove shoes & hang  jackets. Relax in the open living room with beautiful bay window and open dining area.  Galley kitchen with Magic chef oven, Jenaire cooktop, Maytag dishwasher & Samsung fridge.  4 large bedrooms, and 2 baths with original hardwood floors in the Primary bedroom, hallway & stairs.. This home is located on a huge lot with pool & pergola covered in fresh grapes.  The fenced yard is perfect for your fur babies.   6 year old roof, forced air, gas heat, and new 100 amp electrical. Fireplaces to keep you cozy in winter months. Nice size laundry room with sink.  Enjoy the oversized 2 car garage with tons of storage.  Backyard has grapes raspberries and blueberries galore! This is a diamond in the rough,  Potential is limitless!  Welcome home!
